sequenceDiagram
  participant User as Пользователь
  participant FE as Miniapp / site / frontend
  participant G as GLAIM source-chat API
  participant T as source_tokens
  participant Store as sessions/messages/events
  participant Queue as job queue
  participant Agent as локальный агент-курьер

  User->>FE: открывает чат
  FE->>G: POST /sources/{source}/chat/session<br/>X-Source-Secret
  G->>T: validate source token + scope
  G->>Store: upsert project/app/binding/session
  G-->>FE: session_id + next_after_id

  User->>FE: отправляет сообщение
  FE->>G: POST /sources/{source}/chat/messages<br/>client_message_id
  G->>T: validate source token + scope
  G->>Store: persist user_message event
  G->>Queue: enqueue job for agent
  G-->>FE: 202 job_id/run_id/created

  Agent->>Queue: claim assigned job
  Agent->>G: progress / final events
  G->>Store: persist public event projection

  loop пока работа активна
    FE->>G: GET /sessions/{session_id}/events?after_id=...
    G->>T: validate source token + scope
    G->>Store: read public events
    G-->>FE: events + next_after_id
  end
